<div class="home">
  <div class="slider">
   <div>
     <%= image_tag "IMG_8463.JPG" %>
   </div>
   <div>
     <%= image_tag "IMG_7408 (1).JPG" %>
   </div>
   <div>
     <%= image_tag "Hair_Braiding.JPG" %>
   </div>
  </div>
  <div class="description">
    <h4>WELCOME TO MY CHILD & ME INC </h4> <br/>
    <p><strong>HELPING ABANDONNED MOTHERS WITH CHILDREN</strong></p>
    <%= link_to "DONATE NOW", donate_path, style: "border: none; padding: 17px; margin: 15px; color: white; background-color: #d13c3f; font-size: 22px; border-radius: 15px"%>
  </div>
  <div class="who-we-are">
    <h1 style="color: #d13c3f; text-align: center; padding: 15px">WHO WE ARE</h1>
    <div class="descpt-wwa" style="display:flex; justify-content: center; padding: 25px; gap: 20px">
      <p>
         We help mothers help themselves and their children.
         My Child & Me, Inc. is a non-profit organization committed to stabilizing families
         by elevating the quality of life of the abandoned mothers with children
         living in the Democratic Republic of the Congo. My Child & Me recognizes the devastation of war and sexual
         violence against women in the Congo and specifically its impact on mothers with children.
         My Child & Me's mission is
          to provide these abandoned mothers with education, life skills training, and tools to enable them to
         provide for their families and become contributing members of their society.
      </p>
      <%= image_tag "mwabanaimg.png", class: "descpt-img" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="impact">
    <h1 style="font-size: 30px; padding: 25px">OUR IMPACT</h1>
    <p>These are our impact over the years</p> <br/><br/>
    <% if @impacts.present?%>
    <% @impacts.each do |i| %>
      <div class="status">
        <div class="mothers">
          <h2>MOTHERS</h2>
          <%= image_tag "mother-icon.png", class: "impact-icon" %>
          <div style="font-size: 26px"><strong><%= i.mother%></strong></div>
        </div>
        <div class="children">
         <h2>CHILDREN</h2>
           <%= image_tag "children-icon.png", class: "impact-icon" %>
           <div style="font-size: 26px"><strong><%= i.children%></strong></div>
        </div>
        <div class="business">
         <h2>BUSINESSES</h2>
            <%= image_tag "business-woman-icon.png", class: "impact-icon" %>
            <div style="font-size: 26px"><strong><%= i.business%></strong></div>
        </div>
        <div class="workshop">
            <h2>WORKSHOPS</h2>
            <%= image_tag "workshop-icon.png", class: "impact-icon" %>
            <div style="font-size: 26px"><strong><%= i.workshop%></strong></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
    <%else%>
      <div>NO IMPACT </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <h1 style="text-align: center; padding: 30px">FACTS</h1>
  <div class="facts-container">
    <div class="women-in-congo">
      <h2>WOMEN IN CONGO </h2>
      <div class="fact-card">
        <div class="fact-img">
          <%= image_tag "go-green-icon.png", style: "width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain" %>
        </div>
        <p>Violence against women and girls in the Congo are "deep-seated cultural norms"</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fact-card">
        <div class="fact-img" >
          <%= image_tag "go-green-icon.png", style: "width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain" %>
        </div>
        <p>Congo was called the most dangerous place in the world to be a woman.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fact-card">
        <div class="fact-img">
          <%= image_tag "go-green-icon.png", style: "width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain" %>
        </div>
        <div><p>48 women are raped in the Congo every hour.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="children-in-congo">
      <h2>CHILDREN IN CONGO </h2>
      <div class="fact-card">
        <div class="fact-img">
          <%= image_tag "go-green-icon.png", style: "width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain" %>
        </div>
        <p>Parents pay for their children to attend elementary and hight school</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fact-card">
        <div class="fact-img">
          <%= image_tag "go-green-icon.png", style: "width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain" %>
        </div>
        <p>The costs for education are almost as high as the per capital income</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fact-card">
        <div class="fact-img">
          <%= image_tag "go-green-icon.png", style: "width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain" %>
        </div>
        <p>Only 50% of children age 6 - 11 attend primary school</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fact-card">
        <div class="fact-img">
          <%= image_tag "go-green-icon.png", style: "width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain" %>
        </div>
        <p>Cities in the Congo may host as many as 20,000 street children</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px"><button style="border: none; border-radius: 10px; color: white; padding: 10px; background-color: #d13c3f">DONATE NOW</button></div>
  <section class="testimonial-section">
    <div style="padding: 20px"><h1>TESTIMONIALS</h1></div>
    <div class="testimonial-container">
      <% if @testimonies.present? %>
       <% @testimonies.each do |t| %>
        <div class="testimonial-box">
          <div class="testimonial-image">
            <%= image_tag t.image  %>
          </div>
          <h3 ><%= t.title%></h3>
          <div class="testimonial-text">
            <p><%= t.body %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% end %>
      <% else %>
        <div>NO TESTIMONIALS FOR NOW. Will let you know</div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial-controls">
      <button class="prev">&lt;</button>
      <button class="next">&gt;</button>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="news-letter">
    <h1>BE PART OF SOMETHING GREAT</h1>
    <p>Subscribe to our Newsletter</p>
    <form action="">
      <input type="text" placeholder="Enter email addresse">
      <button>Submit</button>
    </form>
  </div>
  <div class="involvement">
    <div>
      <h1 class="inv-title">YOUR INVOLVEMENT</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 40px; color: #d13c3f; font-weight: bold;">THE NEED</p>
      <div style="text-align: start; padding: 20px"><button style="border: none; border-radius: 10px; color: white; padding: 10px; background-color: #d13c3f">DONATE NOW</button></div>
    </div>
    <p class="inv-p">
      40% of women and girls have been raped in the Congo. These women are often shunned and abandoned after sexual assaults. 
      The stigma of rape compels hundreds of thousands of men in eastern Congo to shun their wives and abandon them. As such, many mothers in the Congo are 
      raising families alone.
      These abandoned mothers with children are among the most vulnerable in the society. They live in abject poverty while having to provide for a family, 
      shouldering the burden of shame, physical and psychological trauma, unwanted pregnancies alone.
      These mothers are ill-equipped to raise their children in a healthy environment. As such, sex crimes and child labor have increased among “street children”. 
      The impact of abandonment on these families is a general denigration and deterioration of the family unit as a whole.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="center designed">
    
    <div class="contact-info">
      <p><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> PO Box 673, Ashburn VA</p>
      <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> +15714305030</p>
      <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> info@mychildandme.org</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>